article_title: If Healthcare Prices Emerge, Americans Won't Link To Quality

article_metadata.description: When it comes to healthcare, most Americans -- up to 71 percent -- don't think that prices and quality are associated, according to a new study
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
